_______________________________________________________________________________
"Telepathic Strike" 
        This is, as the name implies, a telepathic attack.  The
        psionicist must first 'aquire a target' by meeting the
        monster face to face (ie you must be 'hunting' it.).  Like
        brainwave, the power is an inefficient attack, costing the
        same as psionic blast but doing less damage.  It substitutes
        pure damage for being able to strike from any distance!
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  6		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  tstrike
